  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Hearty hot and cold buffet breakfast with local produce and served late until 11am on Sundays.</li>
<li>4 course evening meal with choice and including salad buffet </li>
<li>Twice weekly themed evening with special menus.</li>
<li>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included. </li>
