  <description><![CDATA[<p class="p1"><strong>Free lift pass for all guests and free ski school for children up to 17yrs incl saving up to £470 per person!</strong></p>
<p class="p1">With excellent added-value offers and enjoying a quiet location just on the edge of the forest, yet only a few minutes’ walk to the village centre, the Sunstar Alpine is a popular hotel offering the usual excellent standard of service and cuisine of the Sunstar brand. It enjoys wonderful views towards the forest and across the Untersee Lake and offers a daily complimentary shuttle service to the ski lifts.</p>]]></description>
